``.xyz``
 can be provided by a 
``from xyz``
 command in scope.
’ђђЩ Title: title: open
Path: Notes
Content:
Support to automatically parse files with an extension 
``.xyz``
 can be provided by a 
``from xyz``
 command in scope.
